---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="보증 및 A/S 안내 | 데크센터"
  description="데크센터 제품의 보증 기간, 보증 범위, A/S 신청 절차 및 교환/환불 정책을 안내합니다."
>
  <div class="warranty-hero">
    <div class="warranty-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="warranty-hero-content">
      <h1>보증 및 A/S 안내</h1>
      <p>데크센터가 책임지는 품질 보증 서비스</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="warranty-container">
    <!-- 제품별 보증 기간 -->
    <section class="warranty-section">
      <h2>제품별 보증 기간</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">데크센터는 제품 유형별로 차등화된 보증 기간을 제공합니다.</p>

      <div class="warranty-cards">
        <div class="warranty-card">
          <div class="warranty-icon wood">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"></path>
              <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"></path>
              <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>목재 데크</h3>
          <span class="warranty-period">2년</span>
          <p>방부 처리 목재 기준, 정기 관리 조건</p>
        </div>

        <div class="warranty-card featured">
          <div class="featured-badge">인기</div>
          <div class="warranty-icon composite">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"></line>
              <line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>합성목 데크</h3>
          <span class="warranty-period">5년</span>
          <p>WPC 합성목, 변형/변색 보증 포함</p>
        </div>

        <div class="warranty-card">
          <div class="warranty-icon aluminum">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon>
              <polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline>
              <polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>알루미늄 데크</h3>
          <span class="warranty-period">10년</span>
          <p>표면 코팅 및 구조적 결함 보증</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 보증 범위 -->
    <section class="warranty-section coverage-section">
      <h2>보증 범위</h2>
      <div class="coverage-grid">
        <div class="coverage-card included">
          <h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
            </svg>
            보증 포함
          </h3>
          <ul>
            <li>제조 공정상의 결함</li>
            <li>자재 하자로 인한 구조적 문제</li>
            <li>비정상적인 변색 또는 변형</li>
            <li>표면 코팅 벗겨짐 (알루미늄)</li>
            <li>합성목 균열 및 뒤틀림</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="coverage-card excluded">
          <h3>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"></line>
              <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"></line>
            </svg>
            보증 제외
          </h3>
          <ul>
            <li>시공 불량으로 인한 문제</li>
            <li>자연재해 (태풍, 지진 등)</li>
            <li>사용자 과실 또는 부주의</li>
            <li>권장 관리 방법 미준수</li>
            <li>무단 변형 또는 개조</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- A/S 신청 절차 -->
    <section class="warranty-section">
      <h2>A/S 신청 절차</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">간단한 4단계로 A/S를 신청하실 수 있습니다.</p>

      <div class="process-timeline">
        <div class="process-item">
          <div class="process-number">1</div>
          <div class="process-content">
            <h3>A/S 신청</h3>
            <p>온라인 폼 또는 전화(010-1234-5678)로 신청</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="process-item">
          <div class="process-number">2</div>
          <div class="process-content">
            <h3>현장 확인</h3>
            <p>신청 후 2-3영업일 내 담당자 방문</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="process-item">
          <div class="process-number">3</div>
          <div class="process-content">
            <h3>보증 범위 판정</h3>
            <p>현장 확인 후 무상/유상 여부 안내</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="process-item">
          <div class="process-number">4</div>
          <div class="process-content">
            <h3>수리 진행</h3>
            <p>일정 협의 후 수리/교체 진행</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 반품/교환 정책 -->
    <section class="warranty-section policy-section">
      <h2>반품/교환 정책</h2>
      <div class="policy-grid">
        <div class="policy-item">
          <div class="policy-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line>
              <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line>
              <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>신청 기간</h3>
          <p>제품 수령 후 <strong>7일 이내</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-item">
          <div class="policy-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>제품 상태</h3>
          <p><strong>미개봉</strong> 상품에 한함</p>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-item">
          <div class="policy-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"></rect>
              <polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"></polygon>
              <circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle>
              <circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>배송비</h3>
          <p>왕복 배송비 <strong>고객 부담</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-item">
          <div class="policy-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
              <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>예외 사항</h3>
          <p><strong>주문 제작 제품</strong>은 교환/반품 불가</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- A/S 신청 폼 -->
    <section class="warranty-section form-section">
      <h2>A/S 신청하기</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">아래 양식을 작성해 주시면 담당자가 연락드립니다.</p>

      <form id="warranty-form" class="warranty-form">
        <div class="form-grid">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">이름 <span class="required">*</span></label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="홍길동" />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">연락처 <span class="required">*</span></label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required placeholder="010-1234-5678" />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="purchase-date">구매일</label>
            <input type="date" id="purchase-date" name="purchase-date" />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="order-number">주문번호</label>
            <input type="text" id="order-number" name="order-number" placeholder="DC-2026-XXXXX" />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group full-width">
            <label for="product">제품명 <span class="required">*</span></label>
            <select id="product" name="product" required>
              <option value="">제품을 선택해주세요</option>
              <option value="wood">목재 데크</option>
              <option value="composite">합성목/WPC 데크</option>
              <option value="aluminum">알루미늄 데크</option>
              <option value="accessories">부자재/난간</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group full-width">
            <label for="issue">문제 설명 <span class="required">*</span></label>
            <textarea id="issue" name="issue" rows="4" required placeholder="발생한 문제를 상세히 설명해주세요."></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group full-width">
            <label for="photos">사진 첨부 (선택)</label>
            <input type="file" id="photos" name="photos" accept="image/*" multiple />
            <span class="file-hint">최대 5장, 각 5MB 이하</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group checkbox-group">
          <label class="checkbox-label">
            <input type="checkbox" id="privacy" name="privacy" required />
            <span class="checkbox-text">
              <a href="/privacy" target="_blank">개인정보 처리방침</a>에 동의합니다. <span class="required">*</span>
            </span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary submit-btn">
          A/S 신청하기
        </button>
      </form>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="warranty-cta">
      <h2>추가 문의가 있으신가요?</h2>
      <p>전화 또는 온라인으로 편하게 문의하세요.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <CTA text="전화 문의" link="tel:010-1234-5678" variant="secondary" />
        <CTA text="온라인 문의" link="/contact" variant="primary" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  function initWarrantyForm() {
    const form = document.getElementById('warranty-form') as HTMLFormElement;
    if (!form) return;

    form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();

      alert('A/S 신청이 접수되었습니다. 2-3영업일 내 담당자가 연락드리겠습니다.');
      form.reset();
    });
  }

  initWarrantyForm();
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', initWarrantyForm);
</script>

<style>
  .warranty-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 280px;
    background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1600');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .warranty-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 66, 80, 0.85) 0%, rgba(0, 90, 110, 0.75) 100%);
  }

  .warranty-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .warranty-hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .warranty-hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .warranty-container {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .warranty-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .warranty-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-desc {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* 보증 기간 카드 */
  .warranty-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .warranty-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .warranty-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .warranty-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 66, 80, 0.15);
  }

  .featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .warranty-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .warranty-icon.wood {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513 0%, #A0522D 100%);
  }

  .warranty-icon.composite {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent) 0%, var(--color-accent-light) 100%);
  }

  .warranty-icon.aluminum {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B7280 0%, #9CA3AF 100%);
  }

  .warranty-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .warranty-period {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .warranty-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* 보증 범위 */
  .coverage-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    margin-left: -1.5rem;
    margin-right: -1.5rem;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .coverage-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .coverage-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .coverage-card h3 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .coverage-card.included h3 {
    color: #059669;
  }

  .coverage-card.excluded h3 {
    color: #DC2626;
  }

  .coverage-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .coverage-card li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .coverage-card li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* A/S 절차 */
  .process-timeline {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  .process-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 28px;
    left: 10%;
    right: 10%;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-gray-200);
  }

  .process-item {
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .process-number {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent) 0%, var(--color-accent-light) 100%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .process-content h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .process-content p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  /* 반품/교환 정책 */
  .policy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .policy-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .policy-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .policy-item h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .policy-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .policy-item strong {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* 폼 섹션 */
  .form-section {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .warranty-form {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .form-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .form-group.full-width {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .form-group label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .required {
    color: #e53e3e;
  }

  .form-group input,
  .form-group select,
  .form-group textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group select:focus,
  .form-group textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 66, 80, 0.1);
  }

  .form-group select {
